a.xlink:title:
aind_data_schema.core.data_description.DataDescription
Description of a logical collection of data files
Attributes: platform (Union[Behavior, Confocal, Ecephys, ExaSpim, Fip, Hcr, Hsfp, Isi, MesoSpim, Merfish, Mri, MultiplaneOphys, SingleplaneOphys, Slap2, SmartSpim]): Name for a standardized primary data collection system subject_id (str): Unique identifier for the subject of data acquisition creation_time (AwareDatetime): Time that data files were created, used to uniquely identify the data label (Optional[str]): A short name for the data, used in file names and labels. Default is None. name (Optional[str]): Name of data, conventionally also the name of the directory containing all data and metadata. Default is None. institution (Union[AllenInstituteForBrainScience, AllenInstituteForNeuralDynamics, ColumbiaUniversity, HuazhongUniversityOfScienceAndTechnology, NewYorkUniversity, Other]): An established society, corporation, foundation or other organization that collected this data funding_source (List[Funding]): Funding source. If internal funding, select 'Allen Institute' data_level (DataLevel(str, Enum)): level of processing that data has undergone group (Optional[Group(str, Enum)]): A short name for the group of individuals that collected this data. Default is None. investigators (List[PIDName]): Full name(s) of key investigators (e.g. PI, lead scientist, contact person) project_name (Optional[str]): A name for a set of coordinated activities intended to achieve one or more objectives. Default is None. restrictions (Optional[str]): Detail any restrictions on publishing or sharing these data. Default is None. modality (List[Annotated[Union[Behavior, BehaviorVideos, Confocal, Ecephys, Electromyography, Fmost, Icephys, Isi, Fib, Merfish, Mri, POphys, Slap, Spim], FieldInfo(annotation=NoneType, required=True, discriminator='name')]]): A short name for the specific manner, characteristic, pattern of application, or the employmentof any technology or formal procedure to generate data for a study related_data (List[RelatedData]): Path and description of data assets associated with this asset (eg. reference images). Default is []. data_summary (Optional[str]): Semantic summary of experimental goal. Default is None.
